Author: fuckwhywhywhy
Text: I feel this  I’m not exactly the same.. but I do feel like need to like run what I plan on eating by my fiancé nearly every time I eat something and like.... ask him if it’s reasonable to want to eat that or if I should or not  If I don’t tell him/ ask him before I eat, I generally feel the need to tell him what I ate after I’ve eaten it  Poor guy. Surely doesn’t want to hear about everything I eat
